features: 【DESIGNED FOR RTX 3090TI 4070TI 4080 4090】 90 degree GPU 16pin(12+4) 12VHPWR power adapter is designed for GeForce RTX 3090Ti 4070 Ti 4080 4090 GPU. The small 4-pin of the Fasgear Type A adapter is on top of the 12-pin connector, please make sure your GPU's small 4-pin is on top of the 12-pin connector before purchasing. (NOTE: The main image displays two 12VHPWR 90-degree adapters only for the mult-angle view, this item includes just 1 pack of 12VHPWR 90-degree adapter.)

【BETTER FOR YOUR GPU AND POWER CABLE】 16pin GPU adapter right angle can work well with your 12VHPWR 16pin power cable. The 90 degree design ensures that your power cable extends in a suitable direction, preventing it from overflowing the computer and causing improper side panel closure. This makes your chassis more visually appealing. Additionally, using the 12vhpwr adapter reduces the wear of power cable connector and GPU input ports, extending lifespan.

【UP TO 600W OUTPUT & 12OZ COPPER PCB HEATSINK】 Fasgear PCIE 5.0 12VHPWR GPU adapter right angle supports maximum power output of 600W, and 12VHPWR plug is made of alloy copper and tinned material can bring more stable and higher power. This Fasgear GPU 12VHPWR adapter is also equipped with a 12oz copper PCB heat sink to avoid overheating issues.

【EXPAND CHASSIS SPACE】 Fasgear 12VHPWR 90-degree adapter only protrudes 17 millimeters from your graphics card, taking up minimal space within the chassis. Instead, after using the 12VHPWR adapter, there will be more space between the GPU and the side panel, allowing you to install ultra-wide graphics cards in narrower Chassis.

【WHAT YOU GET】 1 pack Fasgear PCI-e 5.0 16pin (12+4) male to female adapter (Type A). Packaged in a paper box and blister box can be sent as a gift. 12-month warranty and 24 hours customer service. If you have any problems or questions about this 12VHPWR Right Angle adapter, please feel at ease to contact with Fasgear team.

【Warm Tips】This type A GPU power cable adapter is not compatible with MSI GeForce RTX 4090 Suprim Liquid X 24G. If you are not sure about the compatibility, welcome to contact us. 【NOTE】 To ensure that the 12vhpwr right angle adapter can be used with your graphics card, please refer to the compatibility list in the product description before purchasing. In addition, do NOT use the adapter with GPU models not listed in the compatibility list.
